Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:59.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Over The Top{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Romance Dawn means the dawn of an adventure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the story of a Luffy slightly different from the one\Nin One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a good sleep! I feel great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that noise?\NIs my boat broken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:03:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? W-What? What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a bird? An ostrich?\NNo, a panda?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm filling the hole with your butt!\NIf I don't, the boat'll sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wound?!\NThen the gunshot earlier was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still! M-My boat... Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a huge ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balloon! Fly away as far as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young man with a straw hat.\NCould you bring that bird up to this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!\NWhy did you bring Balloon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got caught because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NAME: ANNE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Balloon that panda?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a panda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Six Hones Spiel shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain of this pirate ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is this a pirate ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Spiel is\Nan infamous and cruel sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When my village was raided,\Neveryone tried to fight back with their weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they couldn't even get near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.24,0:04:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm, a pirate who attacks villages, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even his crewmembers are afraid of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He destroyed my village and stole our treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All who defy him will be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done. So you managed to catch\Na Ruku - monster bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.37,0:05:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. And you're the kid\Nwho helped us catch it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come down!\NWhat do you want for a reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, boy?\NI'm asking what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:06:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your head's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-M... M-My head's weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:09.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NICKNAME: SIX HONES SPIEL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Were you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, look at his head! It's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock these idiots up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a view! Big ships sure are nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wish I could kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that ostrich yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not an ostrich either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a so-called Ruku, a type of monster bird!\NHis name is Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:07:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been together for\Nas long as I can remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've played and napped together,\Nand never left each other's side even for a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may look like just a bird to others...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to me, he's a more trustworthy,\Nimportant friend than anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...\NThen why have you been kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good question!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah? You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing in that small boat\Nin the middle of the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was seeking out the Peace-mains\Nso we can become friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peace-mains?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a type of pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirates who just lawlessly plunder\Nlike the ones on this ship are Morganeers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Peace-mains go on adventures\Nripping them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna become a Peace-main!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandpa was a Peace-main pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! It's good to be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a man, set out to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's divide the spoils we gained this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Captain! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! Thank me for not losing our way\Non that island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! If I can have this one,\Nit's enough for me this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.35,0:08:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Take a look!\NIt's the best part of our haul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mystic fruit, a Gum-Gum Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:09:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy ship had it by chance\Nand we stripped them of it thanks to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can sell it for 5 billion berries...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a diabolical fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you eat it,\Nyou'll never be able to swim again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be able to swim again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.51,0:09:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, but that's okay.\NI wasn't gonna become a pirate anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay... So you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could've been worse\Nif you wanted to become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are tons of people\Nwho enjoy their lives without being involved with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa... I was lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:10:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I wasn't sure if I could become one...\NBut the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna become a pirate like you\Nand travel to all kinds of places!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the fact\Nthat I won't be able to swim again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you wanna become a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! The sea is nothing like ponds or rivers!\NIt's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if your ship sank\Nin the middle of the sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man shouldn't cry over such a little thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brutal geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!\NHow could you kick your grandfather?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop it! Ouch!\N--You'll become a good-for-nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, so you can't swim.\N--For the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brutal geezer wore this hat all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your treasure, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Balloon is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that! A pod of whales!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just stay here like this!\NI'm gonna get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly. That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. My boat was wrecked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean you won't be able to\Nget out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're driving me crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better stop being ridiculous\Nand save your energy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The key was hanging there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm asking is how you could get it\Nfrom behind bars!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Can you use sorcery or something?\N--No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's kinda close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, help me with rescuing Balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm gonna look for a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Help me!\N--No. It's a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balloon! I'll get you out of there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so lucky! Everyone's having a nap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's showtime!\NHave a one-on-one fight with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you win, I'll release the Ruku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you promise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I keep my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good haul!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found food while looking for a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! That boat looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you underestimate me\Nbecause I am a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, release Balloon as promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Oh, don't do it, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a piece of crap...\NHow could he lose to a little girl like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can let it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balloon! I'll get you out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How naive.\NPirates don't keep their promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't release it.\NI took a lot of trouble to catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lovely day, isn't it?\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend is in a mess.\NWhat are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair looks like a water bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he a fool?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He shouldn't say that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you lying down bleeding?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?!\NI got shot and collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It missed my vital organs\Nso I was waiting for the right moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You insolent brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you show more concern?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:16:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was surprising!\NWhy did you do that all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! He shouldn't have pushed his luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep attacking me?!\NDon't make me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Don't just stand there!\NYour Captain is in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw your limbs stretch!\NWhat's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a riot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when I told you\NI ate the Gum-Gum Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my entire body turned to rubber\Nin exchange for my swimming ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was a true story!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only you can beat him, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to call me Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This pirate group is breaking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I got what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubber Man, just keep expanding\Nand contracting right there forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:18:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Balloon!\N--He turned his back on his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you! Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.69,0:18:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balloon...! Balloon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balloon is said to be the last Ruku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They believe there is magical power in Ruku's blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I got kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:19:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they have me here,\NBalloon will come back again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish he wasn't so rare\Nand didn't have magical power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he wasn't special,\Nhe'd still be my most important friend for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!\NHe's your best friend, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!\NLeave it to a Peace-main!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud of myself.\NI know when to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I fight that monster,\NI would've earned nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need is this bird's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.57,0:20:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can form another pirate group anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ruku!\NDon't try to escape death now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! I wish I could fly like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell did you get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you fool! Don't get on!\NThis broomstick is for one person!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch my hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! The Ruku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ruku...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! It'll be here any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:21:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Don't... Don't... Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I know you saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't there a better way to carry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember! Real treasure is not\Na huge diamond, gold, silver, pearls, nor coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not all the things that only sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, you'll see\Nonce you set out to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is great, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.83,0:22:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you can become a Peace-main!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.09,0:22:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become one at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.51,0:22:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NThis is the beginning of a new journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Several years later, a pirate named Straw Hat Luffy\Nmakes his name in the world of the sea!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.83,0:23:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The treasure ship filled with food gives a rays of hope\Nto the people of Okobore Town!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.63,0:23:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I will make the country a place where\Neveryone can eat as much as they want!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.13,0:23:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Otama sees in Luffy, as he looks to the future,\Nthe shadow of Ace who she misses!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.93,0:23:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.36,0:23:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Coming of the Treasure Ship! Luffytaro Returns the Favor!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
